margin: 0 0 1em 0;">At Breather, we tried a bunch of things to keep our boa=
rd members up to date on metrics, from the standard monthly investor update=
 and quarterly board deck &#8211; which I&#8217;m sure some junior person o=
n their team had to put into a spreadsheet &#8211; to operating models to a=
