d all of that information is squirreled away somewhere in my inbox until I =
take the time to manually move it from email to Airtable. It makes staying =
on top of portfolio companies&#8217; performance a bigger challenge than it=
 needs to be.&nbsp;</p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-he=
ight: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">On the individual level, it&#8217;s a pain.=
 At the system level, it&#8217;s a huge drain of time and resources:&nbsp;<=
